flowchart TD
    A[Website Inquiry] --> B[Lead Created - Leasing Agent]
    B --> C[Schedule Showing]
    C --> D[Application Submitted]
    D --> E[Automated Screening: Credit / Background / Eviction]
    E -->|Rejected| Z[Notify Applicant - End]
    E -->|Approved| F[Lease Generation - E-Sign]
    F --> G[Move-In Inspection - Geo-tagged Photos]
    G --> H[Tenant Portal Activated]

    H --> I[Rent Due]
    I --> J[Rent Collection - ACH / Card / Cash]
    J --> K{On Time?}
    K -->|No| L[Late Fee Automation]
    K -->|Yes| M[Trust Ledger Updated]
    L --> M

    H --> N[Tenant Submits Maintenance Request]
    N --> O[Smart Dispatch - Proximity / Trade / Availability]
    O --> P[Maintenance Tech Completes Work Order]
    P --> Q{External Vendor Needed?}
    Q -->|Yes| R[Vendor Invoice + COI Submitted]
    Q -->|No| S[Job Closed]
    R --> T{Cost Over Threshold?}
    T -->|Yes| U[Sub-Admin Approval Required]
    T -->|No| S
    U --> S
    S --> M

    M --> V[Owner Distribution Processed]
    V --> W[Financial Reporting / Auditor Export]

    H --> X{Lease Nearing Expiry?}
    X -->|Renew| F
    X -->|Vacate| Y[Move-Out Inspection]
    Y --> AA[Security Deposit Reconciliation]
    AA --> M
